			<div><strong>Guild Summit June 2004 Request</strong><br />&nbsp;</div>
		
		
		
		<div>Post below any UI issues OR <b>suggestions</b> you would like to see added or changed.<br />
<br />
I stress suggestions because SoE is looking for this to be a creative session and I would like to keep EQI's envolvement positive.<br />
<br />
/bow<br />
<br />
<b>EDIT:</b><br />
<br />
I prunned down the post to <b>just</b> suggestions, I am sorry to those who replied to someone's suggestion or offered feedback. I am trying to keep this a list of suggestions. It wasnt personal, just keeping it clean. <br />
<br />
and Kenwoodx2 if you go into EQCLIENT.INI you can change what UI is loaded at startup. (its there so I removed your suggestion)</div>
